English(en): Choose a mouse to compete with!

The chosen mouse will give you math problems. Math problems are at the level that the mouse says.
If you solve math problems, you can be tested for your Mathranger qualification.
Korean (South Korea)(to-KR):
고른 쥑쥑이는 자신이 말하는 수준의 문제를 내줄 거야!
문제를 풀면 나의 수학레인저 자격을 시험받을 수 있어!

English(en): Choose a mouse to compete with!
I can add and subtract! Squeak!
I can do multiplication and division! Squeak!
Korean (South Korea)(to-KR): 나는 곱셈 나눗셈을 할 수 있어쮸!

English(en): I know a fraction and decimal! Squeak!

Good job!
The town jjhief will judge you!
